'Cedric's Barber Battle' is an American reality television series that aired on The CW. The show premiered on April 17, 2015.[http://www.cwtv.com/shows/cedrics-barber-battle/ Cedric's Barber Battle Video - Hollywood | Watch Online Free]  It is a barber competition series hosted by Cedric the Entertainer. The first season consists of 10 episodes, however, only 8 aired.
On August 23, 2016, The CW cancelled ''Cedric's Barber Battle'' after one season.
